{"tid":2499057,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"通訊事務管理局突發踩場 就職工盟《理大圍城》放映會作出疑似警告","createTime":"2021-04-21T14:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T14:49:11.000Z","uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6858f21af668cf94fee59e10eec9c7fb8ee0ad","tid":2499057,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCTU/posts/5543857932321101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCTU%2Fposts%2F5543857932321101&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnRx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=a9417a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCTU/posts/5543857932321101</a><br />\n今日下午約五時，電影、報刊及物品管理辦事處好大陣仗，派出六名職員，上嚟職工盟辦事處，要求我地交代嚟緊「理大圍城」嘅放映場次及負責人資料。<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱有權派人落嚟放映會現場，監察我地有無出示放映許可證及檢查參加者身份證。<br />\n<br />\n原來政府有呢個權力，以往唔見佢地有行使，《大公報》出完頭版同Ben周出言恐嚇，就嗱嗱聲要招呼我地，認真俾足面。<br />\n<br />\n由於事出突然，我地同合辦工會溝通後，佢地表示要多啲時間先了解有關部門嘅權力規定，所以今晚原訂放映會延期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n我地重申，坐定定戲照睇，唔會縮，同香港人一齊，風雨中抱緊自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://objects.g0v.social/media_attachments/files/106/103/840/444/642/838/original/588aec6368fc3665.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobjects.g0v.social%2Fmedia_attachments%2Ffiles%2F106%2F103%2F840%2F444%2F642%2F838%2Foriginal%2F588aec6368fc3665.png&h=38fc5108&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a88a3aef26e043ccf20b2aff0ada57347b8bd72","tid":2499057,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bc579617deefc09f4862b0d6c9aa6112ed5e6d","tid":2499057,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"push"}]}